snippet.title: Super Daryl Deluxe - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Releasing April 10, 2018 on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, and PC.

Experience high school again in Super Daryl Deluxe, the last totally normal high school themed RPGvania you'll ever want.

Full theme song: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dCwUGEPAqS0
